  "body": "### Component\n\nOther (please describe)\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (e4a2915 2022-06-19T02:24:29.337547Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (Intel)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nI have checked the corresponding files according to this error ,  i.e. hardhat.config.ts & foundry.toml \r\n\r\nhere is hardhat.config.ts : \r\n'''paths: {\r\n    sources: \"./contracts\",\r\n    tests: \"./test\",\r\n    artifacts: \"./artifacts\",\r\n    cache: \"./cache\",\r\n  },\r\n'''\r\n\r\nhere is foundry.toml :\r\n'''\r\ndefault = { libs = [\"node_modules\", \"lib\"] }\r\n[profile.default]\r\nsrc = './contracts'\r\nout = 'out'\r\nlibs = ['node_modules', 'lib']\r\ntest = 'test/foundry'\r\ncache_path  = './cache_forge'\r\n'''\r\n\r\ni have ensured both of them are using './contracts ' , but the error still persists .\r\n",
